'''軟著陸'''是指经济在过度扩张后平稳地回到經濟适度增长的区间，且回落過程中没有出现大规模的[[通缩|通缩]]和失业<ref>{{Cite web|title=什么是经济硬着陆软着陆?|url=https://business.sohu.com/20110325/n279991761.shtml|author=搜狐財經|access-date=2021-03-05|archive-date=2015-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150423070002/http://business.sohu.com/20110325/n279991761.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當一國的[[通貨膨脹|通貨膨脹]]加劇時政府會试图採取各種措施减缓通货膨胀，如果政策合理，則能順利軟著陸<ref>[http://www.investopedia.com/terms/s/softlanding.asp Soft Landing] {{Wayback|url=http://www.investopedia.com/terms/s/softlanding.asp |date=20210211194344 }}, investopedia.com</ref>。

